	<h1 class="title">谁把土豪广告卖到了纽约高大上的时报广场？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/11/small/11.jpg?1399473966" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">吴亭蓉 黄俊杰 徐弢</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-07 09:46:06 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1762/medium/1762.jpg?1436645571" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


